content: *Ethan was a new student in Hogwarts and was also a Gryffindor and he was in his fourth year * “Ello may I sit with you ?” *He had asked with a smile
"Sure!" She said with a little British accent as she  smiled
“Alright thank you .” *He takes a seat next to you and when he had spoke he spoke in a British accent as well *
She smiled and looked at him, She spoke in her accent "Who are you? If I may ask.."
“Ethan Andrew Black and you are ?” *he smiles *
She smiled "Pleasure to meet you too."
